From: Aurélien Hébert <aurelien.hebert@clever-cloud.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] cppgc: Fix include
Upstream: no

Add <algorithm> to cover for std::remove.

GCC 14 requires explicit includes due to stricter C++20 compliance.
---
 src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h b/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h
--- a/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h
+++ b/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@
 #include <stdint.h>

+#include <algorithm>
 #include <atomic>
 #include <vector>

